<HEAD>Pentagon Offers 26 Choppers for Drug War</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Pentagon said Tuesday it would transfer 26
surplus helicopters to the State Department for use in the
international war on drug trafficking.
   The Defense Department said in a brief statement the 26 UH-1 Huey
